f:\mathbb{R}\rightarrow \mathbb{C}
|\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}f(x)dx|\leq\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}|f(x)|dx
|\cdot|
\theta = \operatorname{Arg}\int_a^b f(x)dx
\left| \int_a^b f(x)dx \right|
\left| \int_a^b f(x)dx \right| = e^{-i\theta}\int_a^b f(x)dx = \int_a^b e^{-i\theta}f(x)dx
\left| \int_a^b f(x)dx \right| = \operatorname{Re}\int_a^b e^{-i\theta}f(x)dx = \int_a^b \operatorname{Re}(e^{-i\theta}f(x))dx \leq \int_a^b \left| e^{-i\theta}f(x) \right|dx = \int_a^b \left| f(x) \right|dx.
